---
title: Steak Frites & Café de Paris Sauce with Garlicky Green Bean Salad
description: Step into the heart of France with this classic - steak frites! Tender beef rump is accompanied by hand-cut fries, with a deeply flavourful creamy sauce to dip in to. This dish promises an unforgettable rendezvous with the flavours of Paris, right on your plate.
